---
// Our Leadership Philosophy — pull-quote block
---

<section class="py-8 sm:py-10 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-[1440px] px-5 sm:px-8 lg:px-[52px] mx-auto w-full">
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[16px] bg-[#ECF1FC] px-6 sm:px-10 py-8 flex gap-5">
      <span class="!text-[40px] leading-none font-serif text-[#2563EB] shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&ldquo;</span>
      <div>
        <h2 class="!text-[19px] text-[#0B1220]">
          Our Leadership Philosophy
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-3 !text-[14px] text-[#374151] italic leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          "Technology alone doesn't transform businesses. People do. Our role is to combine
          technical expertise, practical experience and collaborative leadership to help our
          clients build smarter, stronger and future-ready organisations."
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- decorative dot-grid, matching the mockup's right-side pattern -->
      <div
        class="hidden sm:block absolute right-24 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-24 h-16 opacity-40"
        style="background-image: radial-gradient(#2563EB 1.2px, transparent 1.2px); background-size: 12px 12px;"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
      </div>

      <span
        class="hidden sm:block absolute right-8 bottom-4 !text-[56px] leading-none font-serif text-[#2563EB]"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
        &rdquo;
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
